components.name: Extract Claims CSV
components.description: Reads claims.csv from the local filesystem and emits claim records via XCom for downstream processing.

components.name: Extract Providers CSV
components.description: Reads providers.csv from the local filesystem and emits provider records via XCom for downstream processing.

components.name: Join Claims and Providers, Anonymize PII, Compute Risk Scores
components.description: Joins extracted claim and provider records, removes personally identifiable information, and calculates risk scores for each claim.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after both extract_claims and extract_providers complete successfully.

components.name: Load Claims and Providers to Data Warehouse
components.description: Writes the transformed dataset into the healthcare_analytics.claims_fact and healthcare_analytics.providers_dim tables in a Postgres warehouse.

connections.purpose: Write to healthcare_analytics schema in Postgres

components.name: Refresh BI Dashboards
components.description: Triggers refresh of Power BI and Tableau dashboards after the data warehouse load completes.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after transform_join (and implicitly after load_warehouse) completes successfully.
